  "Description": {
    "English": "A fleshy, compact plant with hair-covered foliage, tending to accumulate a covering of snow. The cupped flowers unfold in response to drops in temperature, allowing pollen to be distributed by driving snow and wind.<br><br>Provides decorative landscaping opportunities for bases.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种肉质蔓生植物，叶片上覆有细毛，表面经常积有一层降雪。杯子形状的花朵会在降温时迅速绽开，并通过风雪传播花粉。<br><br>可以作为基地的装饰景观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "小巧的多肉植物，葉子上有毛，容易積雪。溫度下降時，杯狀花朵會舒展開來，讓風雪散播花粉。<br><br>可為基地提供景觀美化的機會。"
  },
